@baseUrl = http://localhost:6080
@theme = juridico
@topK = 5

### Healthcheck
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Upload documento markdown/pdf
# Ajuste o caminho do arquivo conforme seu ambiente local.
POST {{baseUrl}}/documents/upload?force=false
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=BoundaryRagUpload

--BoundaryRagUpload
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="theme"

{{theme}}
--BoundaryRagUpload
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="tags"

contrato
--BoundaryRagUpload
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="exemplo.md"
Content-Type: text/markdown

< ./samples/exemplo.md
--BoundaryRagUpload--

### Listar documentos por tema
GET {{baseUrl}}/documents?theme={{theme}}

### Obter documento por id
GET {{baseUrl}}/documents/{{documentId}}

### Listar temas
GET {{baseUrl}}/themes

### Perguntas com RAG por tema
POST {{baseUrl}}/questions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "Quais clausulas tratam de multa?",
  "theme": "{{theme}}",
  "topK": {{topK}}
}

### Pergunta por agente tematico
POST {{baseUrl}}/agents/{{theme}}/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "Resuma os principais pontos regulatorios",
  "topK": {{topK}}
}
